name: Orion
description: The biggest fear that night was that it would rain, fortunately the dry branches were a good sign that it had not rained for several days in the place, we waited for night and fortunately the clouds were scarce for a couple of hours, we were looking for the center of the galaxy, but it was not seen, there was only the tail of the milky way and orion peeked out to show itself in the night.
